 background-repeat: no-repeat;">Procurement</span></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.83;">Nikon Group&rsquo;s basic procurement policy, CSR procurement and green procurement are described giving basic guidelines.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Nikon Corporation, also known just as Nikon, is a Japanese multinational corporation headquartered in Tokyo, Japan, specializing in optics and imaging products. Wikipedia\r\nCustomer service: 00 1 800-645-6687\r\nStock price: 7731 (TYO) ¥1,613 +3.50 (+0.22%)', 'Nikon', 'Nikon', 'Nikon', 'nikon_6e51313152');
